title: LMP Automotive Holdings, Inc. Announces "As a Courtesy to Those Analysts and Investors Who Were Unable to Attend This Morning's Conference Call," LMP Is Scheduling a Follow Up Call on October 13, 2020 at 4:30PM ET to Discuss Its Entry Into a Definitive Agreement for the Acquisition of a 70% Interest in New York's Largest Franchise Dealership Group - Atlantic Automotive Group - and New York Logistics and Vehicle Storage Company - Atlantic Central Storage - Together Valued at $608,000,000
